Halcyon Investments , New York investment partnership deal mainly risk arbitrage stock trading , said raised Purolator Courier Corp stake 726,700 share , 9.5 pct , 474,900 , 6.2 pct .
In filing Securities Exchange Commission , Halcyon , whose managing partner Alan B. Slifka Co , said bought 201,800 Purolator common share Feb 3 March 2 price ranging 28.689 34.811 dlrs .
Halcyon , said spent 20.1 mln dlrs Purolator common share , said also acquired option Feb 27 giving right buy 50,000 share 1.8 mln dlrs .
